NG0260:1: gdon chen btsan thabs gzir ba yis //
NG0260:3: rgya shog dug dang tsha bas byug / dbus su gru gsum zla gam gsum //
NG0260:4: gru gsum gdon la zla gam stong *//
NG0260:5: phyi rol lcags mkhar rtsa ba'i sngags //
NG0260:6: yang logs rtsibs la spu gri dgod //
NG0260:7: kha sbyar yab yum lto bar bca' //
NG0260:8: gang gnod rdzas la ling+ga bca' //
NG0260:9: ming rta tho mo snying gar brnag / thod chen
NG0260:10: bcug pa dong du brnag / yungs kar dug brab
NG0260:11: gu gul dang *// dug gsum dang ni mu zi dang *//
NG0260:12: brun gsum tshil gsum gzhob pas bdug / ting 'dzin gsal ba'i phur bu gdab //
NG0260:13: khro tshogs 'od zer gzir myos brgyal //
NG0260:14: gang gdon bskyel ba gdan du 'ding *//
NG0260:15: mthong nas bka' rten mgo nas mnan //
NG0260:16: klu gnyan sa bdag zug pa la //
NG0260:17: phag tshil sbrul brun yin nam dang gla rtsi byug / ga pur mngar gsum bzang drug rnams //
NG0260:18: skar chu dang sbyar khong du gtang *//
NG0260:19: gong gi rdzas bdug gang gnod par //
NG0260:20: tsha tshogs sbong la sbyar la byug / kha dmar glang dmar chus sbyar gtang *//
NG0260:21: snying la dud thun phur pas gdab //
NG0260:22: sri'ur rin chen sna lnga gdags //
NG0260:23: phyugs nad sman lnga skye ru gdags //
NG0260:24: de dag gsang sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0260:25: om pad+ma shri he ru ka ma ha tsan+da ra ga ba sham ku ru /
NG0260:26: pad+man+ta kr-ita badzra kro ta ha ya gri ba tsan+da rak+sha //
NG0260:28: ma me shwa ri pad+ma kro ti hri hri /
NG0260:30: ha na ha na pa tsad na tsit+ta rbad nan /
NG0260:35: gzhan yang las rnams mtha' sdud pa //
NG0260:36: sreg pa me yi sbyor ba bya //
NG0260:37: mi thab dmar po gru gsum la //
NG0260:38: dug khrag tsha ba gsum gyis byug / gang gnod rdzas sam rten drug la //
NG0260:39: ling+ga sor brgyad gan rkyal mnan //
NG0260:40: yam shing seng ldeng mdzo mo dang *//
NG0260:41: tsher gnag glang kal bra skyer se //
NG0260:42: dug ril bag phye mar nag btsos //
NG0260:43: mi rta bya phag sha tshil khrag / yungs kar nyungs nag skye tshe dang *//
NG0260:44: dug sna mtshal dang 'o ma chags //
NG0260:45: mar nag la sogs bsreg pa'i rdzas //
NG0260:46: bdag nyid me thabs dkyil 'khor bskyed //
NG0260:47: me lha dmar ser ra la zhon //
NG0260:48: me dar lcags kyu bka' bstod mngags //
NG0260:49: zhag gsum yar bskul sngags bzlas bsreg / thon nas thal 'jim gnod pa'i khar //
NG0260:51: de nas bsad gzir las 'grub ste //
NG0260:52: de yi drag sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0260:53: om pad+ma ma ha shri he ru ka / ma
NG0260:54: ha tsan+da pad+man+ta kr-ita b+ha na d+ha ha ya gri
NG0260:55: ba / na mo d+he ba tsan+da ra ga pad+ma kro ti shwa ri ma ma trag dun hri /
NG0260:56: g+ha ba sha ri ka dz+wa la ram kha ram kha hi /
NG0260:57: ma ra ya dz+wa la ram /
NG0260:58: ag na ye dz+wa la ram /
NG0260:61: dz+wa la ram dz+wa la ram /
NG0260:63: u kri kri ta ya ra' ga ra ga / a ti u ti ya /
NG0260:64: ra ga ra ga / pad+ma b+ha na d+ha ra
NG0260:65: ga ra ga / gri khrag sna tshogs bsreg byas
NG0260:67: gri ru 'chi ba gdon mi za //
NG0260:68: rims khrag yungs mo dug de bzhin //
NG0260:69: sbal sha bse zhom dze yis 'dzin //
NG0260:70: chud gu a chus sbos grir 'chi //
NG0260:71: sgog skya mu zi gu gul gyis //
NG0260:72: gdon du srub nas rims kyis 'debs //
NG0260:73: ba glang lci ba dang ma shing *//
NG0260:74: bse zho gdon de khrag tu skyugs //
NG0260:75: til dang me tog bdud rtsi yis //
NG0260:76: rang gi bsod nams skyed pa yin //
NG0260:77: khu byug rtsa yis nor 'phel te //
NG0260:79: ru ta chu dag rgya sbos dang *//
NG0260:80: sri yang ku dang lan tshwa dang *//
NG0260:81: pad+ma ge sar na ga dbus //
NG0260:82: bsregs te dud pas rang la bdug / mi yi rgyal po bdag dbang 'gyur //
NG0260:83: khros dang dgra rkun brtse zhing byams //
NG0260:84: bud med kun gyi yid du 'ong *//
NG0260:85: gcan gzan gdug pa can kun byams //
NG0260:87: 'dre gdon kun dang mi gnod bsrung *//
NG0260:88: de dag bsreg pa'i las yin no //
NG0260:89: pad+ma dbang chen yang gsang khros pa'i rgyud las /
NG0260:90: bsrung gzir dang sbyin bsreg gi le'u ste bcu pa'o
NG0260:91: // // de nas yul pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug
NG0260:92: mas / bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0260:94: khyad par nye bar drag po'i las //
NG0260:95: 'khor la rgyas par bshad du gsol //
NG0260:97: bcom ldan 'das kyis khyad par drag po'i las 'di bshad do //
NG0260:98: spu gri lta bu'i sbyor ba 'di //
NG0260:99: dben zhing nyams dga'i gnas dag tu //
NG0260:100: rtsa ba'i sbyor ba rtags rdzogs pas //
NG0260:101: ye shes dpal gyi gtor ma bca' //
NG0260:102: bshos du dkar po'i mkhar thabs la //
NG0260:103: g.yu bad gser sgo gser gyi skad khung can //
NG0260:104: ljang bu dkar po ra lug bya //
NG0260:105: snying dang gzugs tsam de ltar bca' //
NG0260:106: shar du bshos bu gru bzhi dkar //
NG0260:107: ba dan dkar po ra dkar snying *//
NG0260:108: lho ru bshos bu gru bzhi ldem //
NG0260:109: ba dan ser po ra yi snying //
NG0260:110: nub tu bshos bu+u gru bzhi gnag / ba dan nag po ra yi snying *//
NG0260:111: byang du bshos bu zur gsum snying *//
NG0260:112: ba dan dmar po ra dmar snying *//
NG0260:113: bdag nyid dbang chen dkyil 'khor la //
NG0260:114: gying lnga bka' sdod las la mngag / dmigs pa'i bla tshe bkrag mdangs 'gugs //
NG0260:115: rtsa dang srog gcod lus srog 'brel //
NG0260:116: gru gsum rten drug ling+ga brnag / phye gsum yungs
NG0260:117: kar dug sna khrag / 'brub khung gzugs la sngags
NG0260:118: la brdeg / 'od dkar tshub nag me 'bar gzugs
NG0260:119: mthong ba // rang rang gzugs kyi mi rta nye ba yin //
NG0260:120: gsod pa'i rtags byung ling+ga gnyan sar mnan //
NG0260:121: zor 'phang smyo 'bog 'thib dang gri gzir gsod //
NG0260:122: de dag drag sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0260:123: om ha ya gri ba hri dbang pad+ma ban d+ha hri dbang pad+ma d+he ba hri dbang *//
NG0260:125: tsan d+ha rak+sha hri dbang ba sham ku ru hri dza /
NG0260:127: a shug me ri srog la dza /
NG0260:128: hri dun dun badzra ba tri shu la g+h+ri ba tsa pa la @#//
NG0260:130: dgra bo'i snying la khyer b+h+yo /
NG0260:131: tsa pa la mi tri khyair b+h+yo //
NG0260:132: nr-i dun dun srog khug dza dza /
NG0260:133: a shug rtsa ba la g+h+ri na pa la hri /
NG0260:134: li ma dun dun khi shag ru tri /
NG0260:136: snying khrag rngubs dun yun rol yam yam rbad /
NG0260:137: ro myags tshal thum lim ti ti /
NG0260:138: dgra bo ma ra ya rbad /
NG0260:141: kha long ka cho ho thum ril shu la sad tra dgra bo la b+h+yo /
NG0260:142: gying lnga drag po'i sbyor ba bshad //
NG0260:143: gzhan yang chu rgod sbyor ba ni // sngon du rtsa ba'i rtags thon pas //
NG0260:144: chu dar dang ni rgya shog la //
NG0260:145: dbus su yul gyi ser bsrung bri //
NG0260:146: phyi rim rtsa bzhi 'bru bzhi dgod //
NG0260:147: yang logs chu ris zlum po la //
NG0260:148: ming sring bcas pa'i drag sngags dgod //
NG0260:149: kha sbyar yul gyi rdzas kyis byugs //
NG0260:150: thod chen gang bzhugs dong du brnag / dong bu'i zor thun gong bzhin bcas //
NG0260:151: mtshan ma mthong nas yul dbus kyi //
NG0260:152: klu la gta' gzhug zor 'phang bskul //
NG0260:153: sbobs na bsregs shing thab bya gtor //
NG0260:155: de dag drag sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0260:156: om pad+ma b+han d+ha hri dbang *//
NG0260:157: ha ya gri ba hri dbang *//
NG0260:160: ba shang ku ru hri dbang */
NG0260:161: phrom phrom shar shar yam hril /
NG0260:162: badzra yag sha ya ma snying myog / ya ma
NG0260:163: khrag ra hu+u la phrom phrom hril hril shar shar
NG0260:167: ya ma snying myog / ya ma khrag phrom phrom badzra yag sha phrom phrom /
NG0260:170: tsa ra rag seg tram si ba b+h+yo /
NG0260:172: na' ga du+u la na la b+ha ra shas da drag tu phob phob /
NG0260:173: dbab pa chu yi 'khor lo bshad //
NG0260:174: gzhan yang dbang chen las mchog ni //
NG0260:175: ri rgyal sa dang mi yi rgyal po /
NG0260:176: bka' rten byin can dur khrod kyi //
NG0260:177: sa la 'brub khung zla gam bya //
NG0260:178: mtshal dang rgya skyegs tsan+dan byugs //
NG0260:179: gang gnod rdzas la gzugs byas la //
NG0260:180: ming byang snying po snying gar bri //
NG0260:181: thod pa srubs med nang du gzhug / seng ldeng mes bsro tshol chen dang *//
NG0260:182: mngal khrag tsan+dan rgya skyegs dang *//
NG0260:183: gi'u wang bse zho byugs shing bzlas //
NG0260:184: me tog dmar po mchod cing gtor //
NG0260:185: dgra la de bzhin rten drug gzug / dar dmar grol la sum yar mchod //
NG0260:187: sprul pa'i khro chung dmar nag ni //
NG0260:188: lag na lcags kyu zhags pa thogs //
NG0260:190: gang la dmigs pa'i snying skye bzung *//
NG0260:191: bla srog drangs te gzugs la bstim //
NG0260:192: yul gsum gsal bas drag tu bzlas //
NG0260:193: bskul sngags thon nas rang 'og sba //
NG0260:194: gzhan gyi rbod gtong drag po dang *//
NG0260:195: srid pa'i spyi bgegs thams cad dang *//
NG0260:196: gnod sbyin ma rungs pa kun dang *//
NG0260:197: gcan gzan gdug pa mche sder can //
NG0260:198: rwa can la sogs ma rungs pa //
NG0260:199: kun kyang bdag la dbang nyer 'dud //
NG0260:202: zas sna tshogs kyi rten sbyar na //
NG0260:203: snang srid zas nor dbang du 'du //
NG0260:204: de yi gsang sngags 'di lta ste /
NG0260:205: om hri hri pad+man+ta kr-ita ba sham ku ru hri ha ya gri ba ba sham ku ru hri /
NG0260:206: tsan+da tsan+da shri ba sham ku ru hri /
NG0260:207: pad+ma ra ga pa sham ku ru hri /
NG0260:208: hri dbang ba sham ma na ya hri hri dza dza ra ga dun dun /
NG0260:209: dbang chen sbyor ba'i dam par bshad //
NG0260:210: pad+ma dbang chen yang gsang khros pa'i rgyud las /
NG0260:211: sbyor ba rnam gsum gyi le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o
NG0260:212: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis khro rgyal
NG0260:213: pad+ma'i rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa'i bskul ba 'di
NG0260:214: bshad do // hrihrang bzhin chos kyi sku la rang byung ba //
NG0260:215: dmar nag gru gsum dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0260:216: pad+ma 'khyil ba dbang chen khro bo'i sku //
NG0260:217: thugs rje thabs kyi sprul sku bzhengs su gsol //
NG0260:218: bdud pho bdud mo phyi chings bsnol ba'i khri //
NG0260:219: chags med pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan stengs na //
NG0260:220: dus gsum dbang bsgyur ye shes lha yi lha //
NG0260:221: dbang chen khrag 'thung ha ya gri ba'i sku //
NG0260:222: sku mdog dmar nag dbu gsum phyag drug pa //
NG0260:223: zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum rngam 'gying brjid pa'i sku //
NG0260:224: spyan gsum zhal bgrad dbang gi mche ba gtsigs //
NG0260:225: smin ma sma ra ag tshogs me ltar 'bar //
NG0260:226: dbu skra kham nag ral pa gyen du 'khyil //
NG0260:227: spyi gtsug rta mgo ljang gu zil gnon rngam //
NG0260:228: rngog ma dmar po dbang gi rta skad mtsher //
NG0260:229: g.yas dkar g.yon ljang dbus dmar rngam sgra sgrogs //
NG0260:230: sku stod zhing chen g.yang gzhi glang chen ko rlon gsol //
NG0260:231: sku smad stag gi sham thabs bdud dpung 'dul //
NG0260:232: thod rlon tshar gsum phreng bas rgyan du byas //
NG0260:233: sbrul rigs bzhi yis sku brgyan phyag zhabs spras //

NG0260:237: dbang drag me dpung klong dkyil rin chen spras //
NG0260:238: sku la dur khrod chas brgyad rdzogs par ldan //
NG0260:239: dbang chen gdug pa'i spyan rtsa bzlog pa yis //
NG0260:240: snang srid drag po thams cad dbang du sdud //
NG0260:241: shangs nas rlung nag 'tshub ma'i bskal pa 'byung *//

NG0260:247: bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra la skyin thang phob //

NG0260:250: pad+ma dbang chen khrag 'thung mi bzad pa //
NG0260:251: khyod kyi dbang drag phrin las dus la bab //
NG0260:252: sdang dgra gnod byed thal ba'i rdul du rlog / hrih /
